4.Name: ITHU NIJAM Full Movie | Angel Pictures | Latest Christian Tamil Movie
4.description:
#AngelPictures #IthuNijam #TamilChristianMovie

ITHU NIJAM is a 2017 Tamil epic disaster film directed by M. Kumar and Jessy Subash, and stars Vijaykumar, Seetha, Senthil, Vadivukkarasi, Thalaivasal Vijay, Mottai Rajendran, Vincent Asokan and Sundar Selvaraj. The film was produced by Angel Pictures. Filming began in Chengalpatt District in Tamil Nadu in early 2016.

Adaikalapatti, is a village in South India known for its beautiful landscape. Its people lead a peaceful and idyllic life. In such a situation, a series of natural disasters of apocalyptic proportions hit the village disrupting their quiet and peaceful life.

The people in the village are astounded in a state of uncertainty not knowing what to make of it. Scientists are frantic to find answers to these disasters. The plot follows the village's Siddha medicine doctor, Vaithiyalingam, as he attempts to help the villagers to safety amid a worldwide strange happenings of the scientifically unexplained kind.

Adaikalapatti, is continually hit by cataclysmic events. Does this mean an apocalyptic end is approaching? Can their faith save them? Did this village escape from the onslaught of natural disasters? What is the reason behind for the increased natural disasters of apocalyptic proportions all over the world?

1.Name: HALLELUJAH ALL MY LIFE | ANGEL SERAPHS | CHRISTIAN WORSHIP SONG | 4K
1.description:
Hallelujah All My Life - a worship song to the Lord for His sacrifice on the cross and for His everlasting faithfulness to lead His people in paths of righteousness. All our lives, let us sing Hallelujah to the King! 

Listen on the following platforms: 
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/1MLZZFHoDlk31P2jpgeX1P 
iTunes: http://itunes.apple.com/album/id1622318946?ls=1&app=itunes
Apple Music: http://itunes.apple.com/album/id/1622318946

Lyrics: 
Verse 1
You gave direction when there was no map in my life 
Darkness turned bright when you shined your light
You broke the walls of sin through your blood and your might  
Dead bones come to life when touched by your fire

Pre-Chorus
There is power in your name 
There is freedom in your name 

Chorus
You fight the battles that I cannot see 
Took all my shame and gave me victory 
I am grateful for your death on that tree
Glory Glory to the Son who sets me free 

Verse 2 
You made a way when there seemed to be no way 
Crooked paths made straight when you are here to stay 
Colours formed in me when all I saw was grey 
Everything I need Lord, is found in Your grace 

Bridge 
Hallelujah to the King who reigns 
Hallelujah to the One who saves 
Hallelujah to the Son He gave 
Hallelujah all my life I’ll say

In our going out and coming in

He delivers and preserves us

playlist76.Name: ITHU NIJAM FULL MOVIE | Angel Pictures

1.Name: ITHU NIJAM Full Movie | Angel Pictures | Latest Christian Tamil Movie
1.description:
#AngelPictures #IthuNijam #TamilChristianMovie

ITHU NIJAM is a 2017 Tamil epic disaster film directed by M. Kumar and Jessy Subash, and stars Vijaykumar, Seetha, Senthil, Vadivukkarasi, Thalaivasal Vijay, Mottai Rajendran, Vincent Asokan and Sundar Selvaraj. The film was produced by Angel Pictures. Filming began in Chengalpatt District in Tamil Nadu in early 2016.

Adaikalapatti, is a village in South India known for its beautiful landscape. Its people lead a peaceful and idyllic life. In such a situation, a series of natural disasters of apocalyptic proportions hit the village disrupting their quiet and peaceful life.

The people in the village are astounded in a state of uncertainty not knowing what to make of it. Scientists are frantic to find answers to these disasters. The plot follows the village's Siddha medicine doctor, Vaithiyalingam, as he attempts to help the villagers to safety amid a worldwide strange happenings of the scientifically unexplained kind.

Adaikalapatti, is continually hit by cataclysmic events. Does this mean an apocalyptic end is approaching? Can their faith save them? Did this village escape from the onslaught of natural disasters? What is the reason behind for the increased natural disasters of apocalyptic proportions all over the world?

Cover by David Shawn + IFP Worship

This Father’s Day, let us resolve in our hearts to love our Heavenly Father till the end. 

This song was performed live by David Shawn and the Intercessors for the Philippines worship team at the Open Heavens Prophetic Conference 2019 in Jerusalem, Israel where more than 800 delegates from 30 countries attended and were mightily touched by the power of God.

My darling, my darling 
Your honey is singing 
I will be singing and dancing and shouting for the rest of eternity 

La la la la la la

La la la la la la
